The purpose of this plugin is to provide a consolidated and organized management
system for filetype plugins, as well as for using automatically-generated
templates parameterized for various file types. Defaults can be set for undefined
file types; these defaults are restored whenever a buffer is exited.

The following features can be managed by the plugin.
	- Comments
	- Highlighting
	- Indentation
	- Generated header
	- Generated body
	- Generated footer
